getNotificationListenTimeout

public int getNotificationListenTimeout()
                                 throws java.lang.NumberFormatException
Returns the timeout in ms which a NotificationChannel in listen mode is waiting for a connection from the client. A value of 0 indicates an infinite waiting time.

Returns:
the timeout time or 0 if the property isn't specified.
Throws:
java.lang.NumberFormatException - If the value couldn't be converted into an int.
